/ Store InputStringAddr
/ JnS SubInputString

/ Un-comment the next block to test your SubPaintChar subroutine. (Task 3.3)
/ Load FontAddr
/ Add E
/ Store PaintCharCharacter 
/ Load Display22 
/ Store PaintCharDisplay 
/ JnS SubPaintChar 

