/ JnS SubPaintString

/ This is the end of the main program.


/ (Task 3.5)
/ Set Colors
Load Green
Store CharColor
Load Red
Store BackgrondColor

Load StringAddr
Store StringAddrForPainting
JnS SubPaintString

Halt

